metadata.name: Kat #1
metadata.description:
Art nude NFT video . Young and beautiful model Kat poses in a boho style interior. The pastel interior colors are emphasized by the stylization of the video as Astia film from Fujifilm. When creating these videos, I was inspired by the works of impressionist artists, primarily Renoir.
These videos have never been posted before.
Specifications: Fujifilm X T4 video camera. Astia film imitation 4k 60 fps.
To all owners who write to me on Twitter, I will send a 4k NFT video.
